{"tid":136933,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「Minecraft」有無人想玩我個mod server","createTime":"2017-02-27T12:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T10:38:40.000Z","uid":82629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a11d020d7675ce72c95def392a7e2f8c18bf5dc","tid":136933,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"我有個mod server 係之前同班fd玩開 （1.6.4）<br />\n但依家無人玩了 有無人有性趣玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n得幾個要求：<br />\n1) CPU要有番咁上下 （班友起左好多紅石野 唔夠勁會好lag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n2) 會研究下科技野 <br />\n<br />\n3）周不時會開黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋唔會搞破壞<br />\n<br />\nBtw我地係玩開心版1.6.4 forge <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n依家開ser 想招十個巴絲玩住先 <br />\n因為之前都係得幾條友玩 太多人唔知頂唔頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有性趣既巴絲就係度留名啦 過半數 即係有5個人我就會開tel gp 開ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n1)嘟嘟羊 <br />\n2）"},{"pid":"17b1da6ea57fe3a4216ee688a3d8afd23139044f","tid":136933,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df5e839079401de8ade3e408ba0efe605c6040c","tid":136933,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26402f454cd28bd6a902ebd5bcc2543d642682eb","tid":136933,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d870bccb935f45d9afc0d0580d1ab1581f40ff5b","tid":136933,